Share this on WhatsAppSpread the lovePopular deejay, DJ Cuppy, has revealed her feelings about her “friendship” with her ex-boyfriend, Victor Anichebe.
Tweeting that she just spoke with him, the Gelato singer said, “I love our friendship! It took us a WHILE to get here. It’s about realising life is too short for beef. We choose peace + positivity!”
Cuppy added, “Just because you’re two great people doesn’t mean you’re compatible as a couple.”
DJ Cuppy confirmed that her relationship with Anichebe had ended in 2017.
